ginang,

00:40:07.030 --> 00:40:08.590
salamat sa mabait na paalala.

00:40:08.590 --> 00:40:11.250
O baka
ma-miss namin ni Yu'er ang isa't isa.

00:40:18.360 --> 00:40:18.960
Pingyuan,

00:40:19.190 --> 00:40:19.880
